'''拉乌夫·拉希德·阿卜杜·拉赫曼'''（{{lang-ar|رؤوف رشيد عبد الرحمن}} ''Rauf Rashid Abd al-Rahman''；{{bd||1941年||||catIdx=R}}）是2006年[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]审判[[萨达姆|萨达姆]]时{{link-en|伊拉克临时政府特别法庭|Supreme Iraqi Criminal Tribunal}}的主审法官。

拉赫曼是伊拉克[[哈拉布贾|哈拉布贾]]的一位[[库尔德人|库尔德人]]，他是1988年{{link-en|哈拉布贾化学袭击|Halabja chemical attack}}的受害者之一。<ref name="times" />在这次化学攻击中，萨达姆的秘密警察对拉赫曼施以酷刑，他的一些亲戚也在这次事件中丧生。<ref name=mail2014/>2006年1月23日，拉赫曼取代{{link-en|里兹格·穆罕默德·阿明|Rizgar Mohammed Amin}}，成为主审法官。伊拉克媒体曾批评称，被告萨达姆在法庭上未经允许大声说话时，阿明表现地“太过软弱”。此后阿明递交了辞呈。

在阿明递交辞呈之后，拉赫曼成为特别法庭的主审法官。在接下来的日子里，拉赫曼控告萨达姆犯有[[种族灭绝|种族灭绝]]罪，将其判处绞刑。<ref name="times" />与萨达姆一起被判处死刑的还有他的一些助手。<ref name="times" />媒体批评拉赫曼在审判中对萨达姆抱有偏见。

2006年12月，拉赫曼通过旅游签证，举家前往[[英国|英国]]。三个月后申请在英国的[[庇护权|庇护权]]。后来他取消了申请。<ref>{{zh-hans}}{{cite news | url = http://news.163.com/07/0311/03/399A0V6G0001121M.html | title = 审判萨达姆的伊拉克法官逃亡英国 | work = 杭州网 | author =  | date = 2007-03-11 | accessdate =  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070325213438/http://news.163.com/07/0311/03/399A0V6G0001121M.html | archive-date = 2007-03-25 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="times">{{en}}{{cite news | url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/uk/article1527418.ece | title = Judge who sentenced Saddam to death seeks asylum in the UK | work = [[Times|Times]] | author = Devika Bhat, Richard Ford and Ned Parke | date = 2007-05-16 | accessdate = 2008-08-13 | archive-date = 2007-03-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070319171859/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/uk/article1527418.ece | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news | url = http://press.jrc.it/NewsExplorer/clusteredition/en/20070317,thesun-819582147ef26e18aa074b2416b1e649.html | title = Saddam's judge seeks asylum | work = Europe Media Monitor | author = ''[[The_Sun_(newspaper)|The Sun]]'' | date = 2007-05-17 | accessdate = 2008-08-13 }}{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>特别法庭宣称拉赫曼“仅仅是度假”，而拉赫曼本人拒绝对此作出评论。<ref name=mail2014/>

2014年6月16日，在反政府组织“[[伊拉克和沙姆伊斯兰国|伊拉克和沙姆伊斯兰国]]”发起的[[2014年伊拉克北部内战|伊拉克北部内战]]中，拉赫曼被该组织擒获。<ref>{{ar}}{{cite news |last= |first= |date=2014-06-16 |title=الثوار العراقيون: قاضي صدام في قبضتنا.. جهز رقبتك يا «الهالكي» |trans_title=The Iraqi rebels: "Saddam's Judge is within our grasp...Prepare your neck Al-Haliki" |url=http://www.alriyadh.com/945307 |newspaper=Al Riyadh |location=Riyadh, Saudi Arabia |publisher= |accessdate=2014-06-18 |archive-date=2019-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823090357/http://www.alriyadh.com/945307 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{ar}}{{cite news| last= | first= | date= 2014-06-16| title= أنباء عن القبض على القاضي رؤوف رشيد الذي قرر إعدام صدام حسين| trans_title= Reports of the arresting of the judge Raud Rashid that sentenced Saddam to death| url= http://www.alwatanvoice.com/arabic/news/2014/06/16/553633.html| newspaper= Donia al watan| accessdate= 2014-06-23| archive-date= 2019-12-01| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191201164329/https://www.alwatanvoice.com/arabic/news/2014/06/16/553633.html| dead-url= no}}</ref>[[萨达姆政权|萨达姆政权]]前高官[[伊扎特·易卜拉欣·杜里|伊扎特·易卜拉欣·杜里]]在[[脸书|脸书]]上的声明，拉赫曼于6月18日经该组织审判后立即处死。此消息被新闻媒体广泛引用。<ref name=mail2014>{{en}}{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2665360/Judge-sentenced-Saddam-Hussein-death-captured-executed-ISIS.html|work=Mail Online|publisher=Associated Newspapers|title=Judge who sentenced Saddam Hussein to death 'captured and executed by ISIS'|first=Lucy|last=Crossley|date=2014-06-22|accessdate=2014-06-23|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204210022/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2665360/Judge-sentenced-Saddam-Hussein-death-captured-executed-ISIS.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| last= | first= | date= 2014-06-18| title= الثوار العراقيون: إعدام قاضي صدام حسين| trans_title= The Iraqi rebels: Execution of Saddam's judge| url= http://almesryoon.com/%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A8-%D9%88-%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85/499569-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AB%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%82%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%86-%D8%A5%D8%B9%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%85-%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%B6%D9%8A-%D8%B5%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%86| language= ar| newspaper= Almesryoon| access-date= 2014-06-23| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140622015643/http://almesryoon.com/%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A8-%D9%88-%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85/499569-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AB%D9%88%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%82%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%86-%D8%A5%D8%B9%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%85-%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%B6%D9%8A-%D8%B5%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%8A%D9%86| archive-date= 2014-06-22| dead-url= yes}}</ref>伊拉克政府未证实拉赫曼被处死，但也并未否认拉赫曼被俘虏之事。<ref>{{zh-hans}}{{cite news | url = http://news.163.com/api/14/0623/10/9VDS4A8H00014JB6.html | title = 判处萨达姆死刑法官欲化妆逃跑 被叛军抓获杀害 | work = [[人民网|人民网]] | author =  | date = 2014-06-23 | accessdate = 2014-06-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109050434/http://news.163.com/api/14/0623/10/9VDS4A8H00014JB6.html | archive-date = 2014-11-09 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>不过后来其家人和[[库尔德斯坦地区政府|库尔德斯坦地区政府]]的发言人都宣称此报导是不真实的。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://rudaw.net/english/kurdistan/260620143|date=2014-06-26|title=Kurdish Judge Who Ordered Saddam Hanged is Alive and Well|work=Rudaw English|first=Raed asad|last=ahmed|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140626175826/http://rudaw.net/english/kurdistan/260620143|archivedate=2014-06-26|deadurl=no}}</ref>

